Interface TryTrait

All Superinterfaces:

All Known Implementing Classes:
Application, BaseComponent, BaseStringMap, CaseFoldingStringMap, com.telenav.kivakit.internal.testing.CoreUnitTest, Folder, KivaKit, NameMap, Project, PropertyMap, Server, SettingsProject, StringMap, StringToStringMap, UnitTest, VariableMap
public interface TryTrait extends Broadcaster, SilentTryTrait
Provides methods that execute code, stripping off checked exceptions.

try/catch

  • SilentTryTrait.tryCatch(UncheckedVoidCode)
  • SilentTryTrait.tryCatch(UncheckedCode)
  • tryCatch(UncheckedCode, String, Object...)
  • tryCatch(UncheckedVoidCode, String, Object...)

try/catch/throw

  • tryCatchThrow(UncheckedCode, String, Object...)
  • tryCatchThrow(UncheckedVoidCode, String, Object...)

try/catch/default

  • SilentTryTrait.tryCatchDefault(UncheckedCode, Object)

try/finally

  • tryFinally(UncheckedVoidCode, Runnable)
  • tryFinally(UncheckedCode, UncheckedVoidCode)

Examples:

tryCatch(this::start, "Microservice startup failed");
tryCatchDefault(this::computeBytes, Bytes._0);
tryFinally(this::compute, this::report);
